light a penny candle ( 1982 ) is maeve binchy 's first novel , which follows two girls growing up during and in the aftermath of world war ii.   plot summary london was a very dangerous place to live during world war ii , and many children were evacuated to ireland or the united states .

first novels : not surprisingly , ireland is the setting for this " circle of friends " author 's first novel , " light a penny candle "

maeve binchy